# intelligent does

- reposition to not be flanked
- frequently check who is behind them
- takes opportunity to recover
- lets other fighters fight it out
- cheapshot fighters with their backs turned
- defend, block then counter attack
- play defensive when low spirit, energy or stamina
- waits for rampaging enemies to tire out
- patient, do nothing and wait for others to fight

# stupid does

- low situational awareness
  - not recognising an opponent is gunning for them
  - not recognising an opponent is much stronger than them
  - not recognising being flanked
- ineficient energy use
  - attack when low energy
- dodge or block less
- emotional decision, respond to spirit strongly
- missed opportunities
  - when an enemy is vulnerable
  - when they have the chance to recover
